node.text:
I just applied my favorite self-tanning mousse by @getintothelimelight and y’all I feel so good! ❤️ If you’ve been following me for awhile, you know this is my favorite self-tanner and the only one I use. It’s so easy to apply, it’s streak-free, smells amazing, and each application lasts me at least a week! Use my code NILSA when you shop @getintothelimelight and don’t forget to tag me so I can see your glow 😍

Swipe to see the short how to tutorial that I just filmed! ➡️ #lifeisbetterwithatan #glowingskinisalwaysin

node.text:
✨GIVEAWAY✨ One of my favorite Mamas, @cheynotshy has released the cutest jewelry line with @thediamondreserve 🤍 The Mommy & Me Collection has vast array of everyday fine diamond & gold jewelry pieces that allow you to show off & honor your motherhood! I LOVE my Mama Drop Diamond Necklace, & in celebration I have teamed up with Cheyenne & The Diamond Reserve to host a GIVEAWAY. One lucky winner will get their choice of a Mama Drop Diamond Necklace in their choice of white, yellow, or rose gold! A $1,240 prize! OR they can select another piece from the line of equal or less value. Entering to WIN is SO EASY! All you need to do to enter to WIN is the following 3 steps;

1. Follow me 🥰 & show this post some love!
2. Follow @cheynotshy & @thediamondreserve ✨
3. Tag 3 friends that you know would love to enter to win in the comments below!

*This giveaway is not affiliated with Instagram.
*Open to 18+ & US residents only.

node.text:
My Ravioli turned 1 yesterday! We celebrated him by giving him @joeysfamousdogtreats! This company is special to me because my little 13 year old cousin Joey is the owner/creator of these delicious dog treats! How awesome is that?! 13 years old and has started his own company!!!
